# Testing

**Vitest**; colocate `Foo.test.ts` beside `Foo.ts`.

| Area | Tests |
| --- | --- |
| `src/data-model/` | `data-model.test.ts` (or module colocated tests) |
| Shader compilation | `NodeShaderCompiler.test.ts` |
| Automation | `automationEvaluator.test.ts` |

Run: `npm test` / `npx vitest run path/to/file.test.ts`.

**Refs:** Existing `*.test.ts` next to code above.
